<br>
There were some recent changes that is making the feedback process work better between us TLs and Mythic. The respecs for everyone (among other things) is a result of that.<br>
<br>
Obviously no game is ever done, this isn't the last patch, if things are too bad, they will make changes again. And I know it is hard not to be cynical about the whole thing at times.<br>
