<br>
It gave us three things we asked for (all of which I feel were the lowest on the priority list), and improved things in areas we didn't care about, but ignored what areas we wanted &quot;fixing&quot;. It's like they didn't even read the portion of the TL reports, and just &quot;assumed&quot; flank/shadowsrain wasn't doing enough damage, and thus why we were complaining.<br>
<br>
